Business Segments - PennyMac













































Business Segments



























Business Segments


We conduct our business in three segments: loan production, loan servicing (together, 
these two activities comprise mortgage banking), and investment management. Our 
loan production segment is sourced through two channels: correspondent production 
and consumer direct lending. Our loan servicing segment performs loan administration, 
collection, and default management activities. Our investment segment currently 
manages PennyMac Mortgage Investment Trust (PMT) and two private Investment Funds.








