About Us - PennyMac Commercial Real Estate Finance






























Toll-free: (888) 996-5775






About Us








PennyMac Commercial Real Estate Finance (PCREF) is a division of PennyMac Loan Services, LLC, a subsidiary of PennyMac Financial Services, Inc. (NYSE: PFSI). We focus on the origination, servicing, financing and acquisition of small balance multifamily real estate loans between $1 and $6 million.
As a direct non-bank lender with proven leadership, exceptional financial strength, and a common-sense underwriting approach, PCREF offers a new level of certainty and confidence to the small balance marketplace.
Our Vision
From origination to servicing and into the secondary market, PCREF is driven by an innovative team aiming to provide a trustworthy and reliable lending solution.
Our mission is to leverage our experience and proven leadership to stand out in the crowd by delivering the speed and closing certainty the market deserves.












